What I get out of that:<br>
<br>
&quot;i ripped people off as badly as I could, then made another character so no-one would know who i am. then I was caught, everyone found out who I was, and I was kicked out of my guild. so instead of going through the aggravation of making a whole new character yet again, i'm going to just say i'm sorry.&quot;<br>
