2. If some jackass stole your home theater system (HTS being what you could have bought with the ebayed money of plat he got from MQ's), then a month later was busted by the cops (Cops being the angry EQ players), and he said &quot;i'll try to reimburse you people instead of going back to jail&quot; (Jail being levels 1-45 of a new character), would you really give a rat's ass?<br>
