<br>
First, don't make foolish assumptions about how *I* would react to someone trying to make reparations with me for something as &quot;large&quot; as stealing some electronics. You don't know me and perhaps I'm not as vindictive as you are.<br>
<br>
Second, it's not like he's expecting to reimburse everyone he cheated, then immediately have everyone like him. He's done something to his reputation that is nearly irrevokable. Hopefully many people will give him another chance once he's actually made it up to the people he cheated, but even these people will *always* be suspicious of him to some extent. He may get another chance, but he won't get very much trust or respect, if any at all. This is his 'jail time'.<br>
<br>
Third, and most importantly, you don't seem to be grasping that he's trying to put LIES behind him. If he's trying to practice honesty, why the hell would he choose to just create another character, hide, never tell any of his new friends the truth, AND never pay back the people he cheated? And why would YOU even suggest that he should?? I would think that you, being so against his actions, would want him to fix them, not just run and hide from them behind more lies. This suggestion says more about you than it does about him. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/uzenpyrrho.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zenpyrrho</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Scowls at you rdy to attack!</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(6/20/02 1:42:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=112.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re: Dexan's idea</span><hr size=1> I agree, Dexan, a list would be a good idea. It would hold him accountable to us very closely, as well as proving to the naysayers that he's actually trying to work things out (if he indeed is). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/urequiskrist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RequisKrist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Scowls at you rdy to attack!</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#333333>(6/20/02 3:59:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fguild75784frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=112.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re: Dexan's idea</span><hr size=1> I didn't see a single point to rival the ones I made. Sorry. Try again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap w